    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "2012 - Pakistan"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Technology, Information, and the Internet"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Over 10,000 employees"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The Customer"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Daraz is the leading online marketplace across South Asia (excluding India). Daraz provides access to 10 million products and delivers more than 2 million packages every month. In 2018, Daraz was acquired by Alibaba Group.\n\n\nThe business covers four key areas – e-commerce, logistics, payment infrastructure, and financial services – providing sellers and customers with an end-to-end commerce solution. With access to over 500 million customers in various markets, Daraz strives to deliver on its promise of enabling easy access to a wide assortment of products. Together with its digitalized logistics business, it employs more than 10,000 people, helping to bring economic opportunities to communities in South Asia."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/daraz_logo-2.png",
          "alt": null,
          "w": 267,
          "h": 267
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The Problem"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The web portals and middleware apps should be hosted in Azure as app services."
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "They should be connecting with Dynamics AX 2012 hosted on-premise."
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Azure single sign-on for mobile apps and web portals."
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Infrastructure security & Application monitoring."
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Mobile apps build distribution."
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Disaster recovery."
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Folio3 Solution"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "The build and release management of multiple applications, web portals and middle wares wasn’t an easy task. The customer is also required to have a disaster recovery mechanism in place so that in case the primary region goes down everything can be replicated into another region to keep their operat"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "To resolve the issue regarding the production environment, we suggested following these steps for segregation."
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Continuous Integration of all the mobile"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Continuous Delivery for the same is achieved"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Mobile application builds distribution is achieved"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The whole Infrastructure deployment is done"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Azure DevOps automation was employed for"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Azure AD Application registrations were also"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "The automation is being performed for all the"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "A secondary Azure region is also set up for"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
